        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-num">08</div>
          <div>
            <div class="faq-q">What documentation do I need?</div>
            <div class="faq-a">Typically: two years of complete federal 1040s with all schedules including Schedule C; if S-corp owner, Form 1120-S returns with K-1s and Schedule L; all 1099-NECs received (auto/PI, satellite days, etc.); current servicer statement showing actual IDR payment if applicable; profit-and-loss statements year-to-date; merchant processor monthly reports if cash-pay membership; and 60 days of personal and business bank statements.</div>
